# Rested

An interactive CLI tool to build and test HTTP requests â€” fast, clean, and
keyboard-first.

---

## Features

- Create and send REST API requests from your terminal
- Interactive prompts for:
  - Method, URL, headers, body
- Use your preferred editor (via `$EDITOR`) to edit multiline request bodies
- Organize requests into **collections**
- View and re-run saved requests

---

## Installation

```bash
git clone https://github.com/barelydead/rested.git
cd rested
go build -o rested
./rested
```
